short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find Out How Much You Really Use Stack Overflow

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Overflowing allows you to see how much or at least how many times you copy code off Stack Overflow.
The amount of times you copy code and the dates are recorded, and a beautiful chart is created for your pleasure.
